{"tid":1188324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[請廣傳］10小辣69遊行gp","createTime":"2019-06-06T07:37:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T06:16:43.000Z","uid":113373,"like":64,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"f7dc74c1b1ec0d005a6452fb9f594426d04f9691","tid":1188324,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:37:39.000Z","msg":"[請廣傳］10小辣69遊行gp<br />\n<br />\n近日我聽開始聽到一啲之前冇留意開政治嘅人都睇唔過眼想69一齊行，但又因為未行過、冇人跟又唔想跟政黨而淆淆地，所以我地開咗個「全自發無黨派入門級」嘅10小辣遊行group。到時會由無黨派嘅自發連登仔同大家一齊行。<br />\n<br />\nJoin link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/DhV0_xZRYijdtXhf5PPloA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FDhV0_xZRYijdtXhf5PPloA&d=M59wMjr1KB2wSFKn0iQ%2Bgv%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=20a3ba72\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/DhV0_xZRYijdtXhf5PPloA</a><br />\n<br />\n再講一次，無論大家係勇武定和理非，只要真心想為件事好，我地都尊重。今次搞呢個十小辣group只係想6月9號多啲人出，呢個時刻已經唔容許我地再分裂，所以請各派人士請高抬貴手，唔好入去提黨派/屌人唔勇武。多謝！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 如果你係食開中辣大辣嘅，相信你已經有自己嘅朋友同路線，我地就唔多此一舉再開group啦！兄弟登山，各自努力！大家加油！💪"},{"pid":"b861432f5c91dfdc7ac93398ebe62037a5a465cf","tid":1188324,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:43:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ddcd0f3f234d7cb5e77e0fc5f158487d3f2ca1","tid":1188324,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:44:53.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"9ffc9f63de4369a9995e5c19f935b4410f0ceee4","tid":1188324,"uid":45683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T08:05:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"442d90d8750e7d4af27708acd48203dacfdedefc","tid":1188324,"uid":199352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T08:09:42.0